                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": true, 
                    "text": "The current behavior of pushing to DVCS on commit is a bit of a\nthrowback, since I decided a while ago that mr should behave as close to the\nnormal behavior of each vcs as possible, rather than trying to impose\none standard behavior on them all.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": true
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " But I've hesitated to\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "changs the default commit behavior yet.", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": " Which is why the record\nsubcommand command is there.\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
                }, 
                {
                    "is_in_lex_summary": false, 
                    "text": "\n", 
                    "is_in_email_summary": false
